<script>
var heroWrap = document.getElementById('hero-wrap');
var heroTabsList = heroWrap.querySelectorAll('.nav-link');
var heroTabsBodyList = heroWrap.querySelectorAll('tab-pane');
var i;
var j;

var switchTabs = function(tab) {
    var activeTab = heroWrap.querySelector('.nav-link.active');
    var activePane = heroWrap.querySelector('.tab-pane.active');
    var nextPaneName = tab.getAttribute('data-tab');
    var nextPane = heroWrap.querySelector('#' + nextPaneName);

    activeTab.classList.remove('active');
    activePane.classList.remove('active');

    tab.classList.add('active');
    nextPane.classList.add('active');
};

for (i = 0; i < heroTabsList.length; i++) {
    var tab = heroTabsList[i]
    var tabLink = tab.getAttribute('data-tab');

    tab.addEventListener('click', function() {
        switchTabs(this);
    });
};
</script>
